什么事情？

11
00:01:35,686 --> 00:01:36,281
Medok!

12
00:01:36,447 --> 00:01:37,145
Let me go!
放开我！

13
00:01:37,299 --> 00:01:40,072
Medok! This is very foolish of you Medok.
It's for your own good.
Medok！你真是太蠢了，这是为了你自己好

14
00:01:40,253 --> 00:01:41,899
Out of my way!
别挡我道！

15
00:01:43,029 --> 00:01:45,023
He's far too dangerous to be allowed to escape.
他太危险了，不能让他逃走

16
00:01:45,411 --> 00:01:48,616
Get after him!
You should have stopped him!
去追他！你们应该拦住他的！

17
00:01:48,780 --> 00:01:49,632
What happened, Ola?
发生了什么，Ola？

18
00:01:49,817 --> 00:01:52,513
He refused treatment in front of my guards, 
so I dismissed them...
他拒绝在我的警卫面前接受治疗，于是我遣散了他们...

19
00:01:52,673 --> 00:01:54,381
- and he made a dash for it.
- Well get after him.
- 他就趁机冲出来了  - 那去追他

20
00:01:55,006 --> 00:01:56,217
He must not get away!
不能让他跑了！

21
00:03:29,790 --> 00:03:30,417
Hey!
嘿！

22
00:03:31,106 --> 00:03:32,353
Oh! Oh, Ben! For goodness sake!
噢！噢，Ben！天可怜见！

23
00:03:32,844 --> 00:03:35,260
Well, what's the big stick for Jamie?
Nothing's happened yet.

24
00:03:35,450 --> 00:03:38,923
Have you no sense? Have you forgot 
what we saw on that time scanner?
你没有感觉吗？你已经忘了我们在时间扫描仪上面看见的东西？
<i>(通过时间扫描仪可以瞥见未来, 最开始出现在《月球基地》一集)</i>

25
00:03:39,122 --> 00:03:40,252
Don't, it was horrible.
别，那太可怕了

26
00:03:40,414 --> 00:03:43,466
Aye, well, I'll not being left without nothing
to defend ourselves with.

27
00:03:43,649 --> 00:03:45,217
I'm afraid you're wasting your time, Jamie.
我觉得你恐怕是在浪费自己的时间，Jamie

28
00:03:45,425 --> 00:03:46,082
Why?
怎么说？

29
00:03:46,468 --> 00:03:50,271
Unless I'm very much mistaken, 
these creatures are so big...
除非我错得离谱，这些怪物如此之大...

30
00:03:50,321 --> 00:03:52,671
they're going to see us long before we see them.
在我们看见它们之前，它们就先看见我们了

31
00:03:53,142 --> 00:03:53,856
Look out Jamie!
小心，Jamie！

32
00:03:54,447 --> 00:03:55,777
Hang on, mate, I'll get him!
坚持，伙计，我来fixme

33
00:03:58,983 --> 00:03:59,511
Ben!

34
00:04:00,326 --> 00:04:01,151
Sit on top of him!

35
00:04:03,725 --> 00:04:04,612
What are you doing?_!
你在做什么？

36
00:04:05,754 --> 00:04:06,904
Ben, are you all right?
Ben，你没事吧？

37
00:04:13,777 --> 00:04:17,365
We don't know who you are, strangers,
but we are grateful. 
虽然我们不认识，异乡人，但我们很感激

38
00:04:17,756 --> 00:04:20,365
Medok is one of our last patients in the Colony.
Medok 是这个殖民地仅有的几个病人之一

39
00:04:20,775 --> 00:04:25,240
We've done our best for him
but he gets worse day by day...
我们已经为他尽了最大的努力, 但他的情况一天比一天差

40
00:04:29,102 --> 00:04:32,340
I wasn't informed you were 
travelling across our territory.
我没有收到信息说你们正在我们的领土上旅行

41
00:04:34,311 --> 00:04:37,322
Hurry back to the Colony 
and tell the Pilot what's happened.
赶紧回到殖民地，告知领航员这里发生的情况

42
00:04:38,045 --> 00:04:38,974
Pilot?
领航员？

43
00:04:39,388 --> 00:04:44,415
Yes, the Pilot of our colony. No doubt
he will want to thank you in person.
是的，我们殖民地的领航员。毫无疑问他会想要亲自感谢你

44
00:04:45,330 --> 00:04:48,960
Tie him up tighter. Come on, tighter! 
I don't want any more trouble with him. 
把他绑紧点。使劲，紧点！我不想让他再惹麻烦了

45
00:04:49,023 --> 00:04:51,260
Come on, I'll show you myself. Get out of...

46
00:04:52,574 --> 00:04:56,053
Er, uh, any good asking where we are?
呃，我想问问我们是在哪儿？

47
00:04:56,449 --> 00:05:00,060
Well, according to my calculations 
we're, er, certainly in the future and, 
根据我的计算，我们是在...当然是在未来，而且...

48
00:05:00,201 --> 00:05:04,124
- er, on a planet very like the Earth.
- How do you know?
- 在一个跟地球非常相似的星球上  - 你怎么知道？

49
00:05:04,386 --> 00:05:06,608
I don't know. I'm guessing.
我不知道，只是猜测

50
00:05:07,189 --> 00:05:09,981
My name is Ola. I am the Chief of Police.
我名叫 Ola，是这里的警察局长

51
00:05:10,212 --> 00:05:11,569
That sounds very important.
这听起来是个重要人物

52
00:05:11,833 --> 00:05:17,465
Oh, it's a very responsible job. 
I take my instructions from our Control centre. 
噢，这是个很需要责任的工作。我听从我们控制中心的指令

53
00:05:17,756 --> 00:05:23,456
Oh, it all works very well, as you will see. 
Please follow me.
噢，它运作得很好，你们会看到的。请跟我来

54
00:05:24,131 --> 00:05:25,020
Oh, thank you.
噢，谢谢你

55
00:05:29,535 --> 00:05:32,730
Ah, not too tight l?
It's bad for the blood pressure.
啊，不要太紧了。这样对血压不好

56
00:05:36,094 --> 00:05:37,501
"Run, run, run, run...
“跑跑跑跑...

57
00:05:37,856 --> 00:05:38,210
Run, run, run, run!
跑跑跑跑！

58
00:05:39,114 --> 00:05:40,190
Thank you shift...

59
00:05:40,759 --> 00:05:41,793
Thank you shift...

60
00:05:42,573 --> 00:05:43,400
Number one!

61
00:05:48,510 --> 00:05:50,184
Pilot, these are the strangers
that have helped us.
领航员，这就是刚才帮助了我们的几位异乡人

62
00:05:50,614 --> 00:05:52,050
Very well, Ola. I will look after our guests. 
很好，Ola。我来招待我们的客人

63
00:05:52,135 --> 00:05:55,010
You will no doubt wish to take care of poor Medok. 
You may leave.
毫无疑问你想要去照顾可怜的Medok。你可以走了

64
00:05:55,963 --> 00:05:59,451
Well, our thanks to you and welcome! 
我们感谢你们，也欢迎你们的到来！

65
00:05:59,678 --> 00:06:02,451
You are indeed a brave man
to tackle someone as disturbed as Medok.
你真是一个勇敢的人，能对付像 Medok 这样失常的人

66
00:06:02,780 --> 00:06:05,472
Well, it was nothing. 
Anyone would have done the same.
这没什么，谁都会这么做的 

67
00:06:05,789 --> 00:06:08,772
Well this is gay! Why all the music?
这里很欢乐啊，为什么到处都是音乐？

68
00:06:09,221 --> 00:06:10,765
Oh, we regulate our day by music.
噢，我们通过音乐来调节我们的一天

69
00:06:11,146 --> 00:06:11,752
Oh.
哦

70
00:06:12,111 --> 00:06:12,621
Yes...
是的

71
00:06:12,919 --> 00:06:16,118
...and now my friends, I suggest you 
take advantage of our refreshing department.
现在我的朋友们, 我建议你们利用一下我们的充能部门

72
00:06:16,397 --> 00:06:17,955
Oh, lead me to it mate. I'm starving.
哦，带我去吧朋友，我饿死了

73
00:06:18,237 --> 00:06:21,309
Oh, you will eat later. 
Here we revive the weary body.
哦，你可以稍后再吃东西。这是我们让疲劳的身体恢复精力的地方

74
00:06:21,878 --> 00:06:22,584
Oh.
哦

75
00:06:23,322 --> 00:06:24,487
Keep your eyes skinned.

76
00:06:24,780 --> 00:06:25,670
Why? What's the matter?
为什么？什么情况？

77
00:06:25,892 --> 00:06:28,528
Well, they're a weird sort of folk. 
I don't know that I understand them.

78
00:06:33,851 --> 00:06:36,479
Come along in, my friends, It's just through _ there.

79
00:06:37,246 --> 00:06:39,968
Pilot! Pilot! Control wish you to call them immediately./
领航员！领航员！管理员期望你立即跟他联系

80
00:06:40,046 --> 00:06:41,168
They wish to welcome our guests.
他们想要给我的客人一个欢迎仪式

81
00:06:41,352 --> 00:06:42,280
Oh, but of course.
噢，这是当然

82
00:06:42,475 --> 00:06:43,736
Switch on please, my dear.
请打开吧，亲爱的

83
00:06:47,387 --> 00:06:50,019
Hey, who's that? He looks smashing.

84
00:06:50,196 --> 00:06:51,515
That's our Controller.
这是我们的管理员

85
00:06:53,378 --> 00:06:57,293
We wish to welcome joyfully the visitors to our colony. /57

86
00:06:57,378 --> 00:07:01,293
We are very grateful to them.
They have performed a valuable service. /01

87
00:07:01,378 --> 00:07:06,293
The Colony is to make our guests happy 
and contented during their stay. /06

88
00:07:06,378 --> 00:07:11,293
Welcome again, friends. Now, back to work, everyone!

89
00:07:11,717 --> 00:07:14,749
Well that's great! I'm really going to enjoy myself.
那太好了！我还真想一个人待会儿

90
00:07:15,006 --> 00:07:19,156
Splendid! And now my good friends,
let me put you into the hands of our supervisor, Barney.
太棒了！现在我的好朋友们，我就把你们交到我们的监管员 Barney 手里了

91
00:07:19,528 --> 00:07:21,327
Dear old Barney, everybody calls him.
亲爱的老 Barney，每个人都这么叫他

92
00:07:21,527 --> 00:07:22,405
Well, thank you Pilot.
哦，谢谢你领航员

93
00:07:22,660 --> 00:07:25,697
And I must leave you for... work calls you know, 
and hard work never hurt anybody.
我必须让你...工作在呼唤你知道吧, 努力工作总是不会有坏处的

94
00:07:25,902 --> 00:07:27,610
Till later!

95
00:07:27,941 --> 00:07:29,991
Delighted to see you. Delighted to have you with us.
很高兴见到你们，很高兴你们跟我们在一起。


96
00:07:30,041 --> 00:07:31,991
Now you have a complete choice of all our treatments. 
现在你们可以选择我们所有的休闲方式

97
00:07:32,100 --> 00:07:36,891
We have steam baths, beauty treatments, perhaps a massage. /36.9
我们有蒸汽浴，美容护理，还有按摩。

98
00:07:36,900 --> 00:07:39,091
You sir, of course, would like your clothes cleaned.
先生你，当然了，可以要求把衣服清洗干净

99
00:07:39,318 --> 00:07:43,507
And there's sunlight treatment, moonlight treatment, 
sparkling and effervescent sprays...
还有日光护理, 月光护理, 起泡喷剂...

100
00:07:43,726 --> 00:07:45,428
I feel perfectly all right as I am, thank you.
我现在就觉得非常好，谢谢你了

101
00:07:45,619 --> 00:07:50,389
Ah, go on Doctor. Don't be such a drag. 
It all looks super. Please, may I have a shampoo?
啊, 去啊博士。不要这样的勉强。一切都超级棒的。请给我洗发水好吗？

102
00:07:50,653 --> 00:07:52,032
Shampoo, of course, for the young lady.
当然，洗发香波提供给年前女士

103
00:07:52,223 --> 00:07:52,994
Thanks very much.
非常感谢

104
00:07:53,176 --> 00:07:56,593
And for the young gentlemen, our very 
latest treatment in our cubicles over there.
对于年轻的绅士，那边是本包间提供的最后一道护理

105
00:07:56,896 --> 00:08:01,502
Me? Oh, hey, you're not going to do that to me. I'm no lassie.
我吗？哦，嘿，你可别对我来这个，我可不是个姑娘

106
00:08:01,849 --> 00:08:06,099
It's no good, Jamie, the lassies have got you! 
And believe me mate, I'm not going to struggle.
没用的，Jamie，姑娘们抓住你了。而且相信我朋友，我可不打算挣扎

107
00:08:06,566 --> 00:08:09,210
And now sir, for you...
现在，到你了先生

108
00:08:11,059 --> 00:08:17,903
Oh, very nice. Very nice indeed. You must certainly be 
the most beautiful young lady in our Colony  /17.9
哦，很好，真的非常好。你肯定是我们殖民地最年轻漂亮的女士

109
00:08:18,000 --> 00:08:20,503
and are quite sure to be elected our next beauty president.
肯定可以赢得下一届的选美冠军

110
00:08:20,823 --> 00:08:21,856
Thank you very much.
太感谢你了

111
00:08:22,054 --> 00:08:24,504
Oh, not at all. It's all part of our service.
哦，完全不用。这都是我们服务的一部分

112
00:08:28,888 --> 00:08:29,822
To your liking sir?
你还喜欢吗，先生？

113
00:08:30,185 --> 00:08:32,322
Ah, marvellous. Like being at anchor in the Med.

114
00:08:32,549 --> 00:08:35,614
Some protective oils for our guests and a little suntan.
给我们的客人来点防晒霜, 再让他们晒黑点

115
00:08:35,972 --> 00:08:37,541
Ha ha! This is the life.
哈哈！这才是生活

116
00:08:39,064 --> 00:08:44,388
Hey mister, would you call the ladies off?
I'm frightened what they might do to me.
嘿先生, 你能把女士们叫走吗？我有点害怕她们会对我做点什么

117
00:08:44,569 --> 00:08:46,092
But you look charming, sir. Charming.
但你看起来太有魅力了, 先生, 太有魅力

118
00:08:46,280 --> 00:08:47,921
That's what I'm frightened of.
我就是害怕这个

119
00:08:55,216 --> 00:08:57,262
Please get me out of here! I'm done to a turn!
请带我离开这里！fixme

120
00:08:57,591 --> 00:08:58,650
Clothes reviver.
衣服翻新器

121
00:08:58,977 --> 00:09:00,275
My clothes don't need reviving!
我的衣服不需要翻新！

122
00:09:00,506 --> 00:09:06,937
Oh, while we're about it, sir... and off.
噢, 我们正要...先生..关掉了

123
00:09:12,848 --> 00:09:15,655
Oh, Doctor. You look gorgeous!
噢, 博士, 你看来很炫！

124
00:09:15,941 --> 00:09:17,152
Oh, my shoes!
哦, 我的鞋子！

125
00:09:17,334 --> 00:09:19,453
Oh, they're fantastic. You can see your face in them.
它们太亮了．你都能在里面看见你的脸

126
00:09:19,648 --> 00:09:22,956
Precisely. Who wants to see their face
in a pair of suede shoes?
的确．谁想要用鞣皮鞋子来当镜子？

127
00:09:23,306 --> 00:09:24,260
What's this one?
这一个是什么？

128
00:09:24,463 --> 00:09:27,507
Oh, that, sir, is our rough and tumble machine,
for toning up the muscles.
哦, 先生, 那个是我们的打斗机器, 增强肌肉用的

129
00:09:27,715 --> 00:09:29,258
Exactly what I need!
正是我需要的

130
00:09:29,428 --> 00:09:30,157
Full on!
马力全开！

131
00:09:30,321 --> 00:09:31,506
Oh, but no, sir! No!
噢, 不要, 先生！别这样！

132
00:09:31,761 --> 00:09:33,034
Turn it off.
关掉它

133
00:09:33,563 --> 00:09:34,616
Come out of it!
出来吧

134
00:09:35,111 --> 00:09:36,630
Come out of it, Doctor.
出来吧, 博士

135
00:09:46,021 --> 00:09:50,938
Oh, oh, I feel better. Oh, that's what I need.
噢, 噢, 我觉得好点了．噢, 我正需要这个

136
00:09:52,205 --> 00:09:58,578
Oh, you look smashing. You really do.
You look like a prince./
噢, 你看起来很兴奋, 真的．看起来像个王子

137
00:09:58,705 --> 00:10:02,578
Jamie that's super. It really is.
Jamie, 那个很厉害, 真的很厉害

138
00:10:03,945 --> 00:10:10,152
Come on, move back! This prisoner's not to be trusted.
He's violent and suffering from delusions.
快点, 回来！那个囚犯不可信, 他很暴力而且还有幻觉

139
00:10:10,478 --> 00:10:16,034
I'm not the one suffering from delusions, it's you!
All of you!/?
我可以不是受幻觉影响的人, 你才是！你们全部都是！

140
00:10:16,478 --> 00:10:18,034
You don't know what's happening in this Colony!
你们不知道这个殖民地在发生什么！

141
00:10:18,212 --> 00:10:19,125
Be quiet Medok!
安静, Medok!

142
00:10:19,288 --> 00:10:21,057
There's only one way to silence me, Ola.
只有一种方法让我安静, Ola

143
00:10:21,222 --> 00:10:24,689
Medok, old fellow, it's Questa. Remember me?
What's happened to you?
Medok, 老伙计, 我是 Questa, 记得我吗？你怎么了？

144
00:10:24,872 --> 00:10:26,724
It's no good. You can't reason with him.
这样没用的．你没法跟他讲道理的

145
00:10:26,871 --> 00:10:29,008
Just a minute. He's an old friend. One of the best.
请等一下．他是一个老朋友, 最好的那种

146
00:10:29,240 --> 00:10:29,703
Ha!
哈！

147
00:10:29,899 --> 00:10:33,322
He's as cheerful as any of us.
Medok, what's happened to you?/?
他以前跟我们一样快活, Medok, 你身上发生了什么？

148
00:10:33,899 --> 00:10:35,322
What's all this about you seeing things?
说你有幻视, 这是在说什么？

149
00:10:35,731 --> 00:10:37,094
I don't see things Questa, you fool!
我没有幻视, Questa, 你个傻瓜！

150
00:10:37,731 --> 00:10:44,094
There are things... horrible things... creatures,
infesting this camp at night.
有一些东西...可怕的东西...有一些生物, 在晚上侵袭这个营地

151
00:10:44,304 --> 00:10:48,885
That's enough! Have you seen the Pilot?
够了！你见过领航员了吗？

152
00:10:49,090 --> 00:10:51,400
He's with the strangers. I've no idea where they are.
他跟那几个异乡人在一起．我不知道他们在哪儿

153
00:10:51,620 --> 00:10:59,641
Back to work! Shift rest is over!
No time to be lost! The Colony needs you!/?
回去工作！轮班休息已经结束了！没有时间可以浪费！殖民地需要你！

154
00:11:00,020 --> 00:11:05,641
Preparation to be made for tonight's reception
- a welcome for the strangers!
还要准备今晚招待会呢 - 要为那些异乡人准备一个迎新会

155
00:11:05,865 --> 00:11:08,249
A reception tonight! A Colony party!
今晚有招待会！全殖民地欢庆会！

156
00:11:08,365 --> 00:11:10,749
Medok, join in with the rest of us, like you used to.
Medok, 加入我们一起来吧, 就像以前一样

157
00:11:10,942 --> 00:11:13,160
It will be fun for all!
将是所有人的fixme

158
00:11:13,633 --> 00:11:14,437
You hear that Medok, fun for all.
你听到了吧 Medok, 大家都很高兴

159
00:11:15,607 --> 00:11:22,036
All right! Have fun while you can,
before they crawl all over you!
算了吧！就尽情玩乐吧, 趁着你们还能, 趁着它们还没有从你们头上爬过！

160
00:11:22,225 --> 00:11:24,623
That's enough! Right, get back all of you.
不许胡说了！好了, 你们都回去吧

161
00:11:24,980 --> 00:11:27,921
There you are. I wondered what had happened to you.
起来吧．我想知道你发生了什么情况

162
00:11:28,165 --> 00:11:30,335
I don't know you. You don't belong here.
我不认识你, 你不属于这里

163
00:11:30,534 --> 00:11:31,740
Do you belong here?
你属于这里吗？

164
00:11:31,983 --> 00:11:34,281
No, not any more.
不, 不再是了

165
00:11:34,482 --> 00:11:37,491
We don't talk to him. He sees things. Come on Medok.
我们不要跟他说话, 他有幻视．来吧 Medok

166
00:11:52,845 --> 00:11:53,731
Can I help you?
有什么可以帮助你的？

167
00:11:55,308 --> 00:11:57,914
What? Oh, no. No, it's all right, thank you./?
什么？哦, 不, 不用．没事的, 谢谢

168
00:11:58,008 --> 00:12:00,414
I... I just thought I'd dropped something, that's all.
我...我只是觉得我掉了东西, 仅此而已

169
00:12:16,439 --> 00:12:17,343
Ha! What's _?
哈！什么东西？

170
00:12:17,898 --> 00:12:19,288
Shh, I'm going to set you free.
嘘, 我正打算放了你

171
00:12:20,771 --> 00:12:26,186
Just hold still a minute. There we are. One more.
暂时不要动．这样．还有一个

172
00:12:28,682 --> 00:12:30,531
Don't bother to say thank you./?
没必要说谢谢

173
00:12:30,682 --> 00:12:35,531
Now, tell me something about these things
that you see, hmm?
现在, 告诉我关于你所看到的东西, 嗯？

174
00:12:36,682 --> 00:12:42,531
Do they, for instance, appear to
crawl slowly over the ground?
比如说, 它们是不是看起来是在地上爬行的？

175
00:12:42,789 --> 00:12:43,697
How do you know?
你怎么知道？

176
00:12:43,947 --> 00:12:45,133
Oh, just wondered that's all.
噢, 只是好奇而已

177
00:12:46,177 --> 00:12:47,108
Listen!
听！

178
00:12:47,710 --> 00:12:49,477
I don't hear anything.
我什么也没听见

179
00:12:49,808 --> 00:12:50,846
Someone's coming.
有人来了

180
00:12:51,091 --> 00:12:52,572
It's all right, I won't let them hurt you.
没事的, 我不会允许他们伤害你

181
00:12:52,755 --> 00:12:53,845
Get out of my way!
别挡我的路！

182
00:12:54,094 --> 00:12:55,062
Why don't you listen to me?
你怎么不听我说呢？

183
00:12:55,250 --> 00:12:56,694
I am not being caught!
我不想被抓住！

184
00:12:59,236 --> 00:13:00,348
Stop him! Don't let him escape!
拦住他！别让他逃走了！

185
00:13:00,839 --> 00:13:02,420
How did he get away? Who's responsible?
他怎么逃脱的？谁的责任？

186
00:13:06,175 --> 00:13:06,775
What happened?
发生了什么？

187
00:13:06,983 --> 00:13:10,138
I... I told him he wouldn't get hurt
and he wouldn't believe me.
我...我跟他说他不会受到伤害的, 但他不相信我

188
00:13:10,336 --> 00:13:11,534
You mean you let him go?
你是说, 是你放他走的？

189
00:13:11,751 --> 00:13:13,608
Well, no, not exactly.
哦, 不是, 不全是

190
00:13:13,919 --> 00:13:17,726
He let the prisoner escape.
That is a crime in this Colony.
他放走了囚犯．这在殖民地是犯罪

191
00:13:17,919 --> 00:13:19,726
For that, men must work in the pit. Guard!
为此, 他必须进入地窖(fixme)去工作．警卫！

192
00:13:19,975 --> 00:13:22,295
You can't touch him. He doesn't know your laws!
你不能碰他, 他不知道你们的法律！

193
00:13:22,456 --> 00:13:24,523
Er, that's true, Ola. He is a stranger here.
呃, 那倒是真的, Ola．他是个异乡人

194
00:13:24,672 --> 00:13:28,883
There's something else you're forgetting gentlemen -
I set free someone that we caught in the first place.
还有些事情你们忘了, 先生们 - 我放走的人之前是我们抓住的

195
00:13:29,052 --> 00:13:30,937
True - a reasonable point of view, Ola.
也是真的 - 这个观点挺有道理, Ola 

196
00:13:31,112 --> 00:13:34,538
Medok is dangerous. He should have never let him go./?
Medok 很危险．他无论如何不应该放走他的

197
00:13:34,612 --> 00:13:37,538
The Colony will be petrified
when they know he's out there in the night.
整个殖民地的人都会惴惴不安的, 如果他们知道夜里他还在外面

198
00:13:37,689 --> 00:13:39,860
Well, send your patrol after him.
He can't have got far.
好吧, 派你的巡逻队去追他．他不可能跑远的

199
00:13:40,017 --> 00:13:43,882
He can run you know. He's got legs.
He doesn't have to crawl over the ground.
他能跑你知道吗, 他有脚．他不必在地上爬着走

200
00:13:44,028 --> 00:13:45,184
Why did you say that?
你为什么这么说？

201
00:13:45,353 --> 00:13:47,649
Why, no reason. No reason at all.
为什么？没有为什么．完全没有原因

202
00:13:47,847 --> 00:13:53,695
Anyone who spreads that kind of rumour in this Colony
will find himself in the hospital for correction.
任何人在殖民地散播这种谣言, 结果都会发现自己在医院里进行矫正

203
00:13:53,869 --> 00:13:56,879
Oh... oh, that's where Medok is, is it?
噢...噢, 那就是 Medok 待的地方, 是吗？

204
00:13:57,130 --> 00:14:01,937
I think, Doctor, you will understand more about Medok
if you talk to some of the people who knew him best.
我觉得, 博士, 如果你跟最熟悉 Medok 的人多聊聊, 你会更加了解他的

205
00:14:02,099 --> 00:14:02,745
Pilot, I think...
领航员, 我觉得...

206
00:14:02,918 --> 00:14:04,215
Now take the strangers to the labour centre Ola.
现在带这些异乡人到劳动中心去, Ola

207
00:14:04,318 --> 00:14:08,215
See they learn something about us.
Please, go with him.
确保他们对我们多一些了解．请, 跟他走吧

208
00:14:08,388 --> 00:14:09,574
Oh, well thank you.
哦, 好吧, 谢谢你

209
00:14:29,279 --> 00:14:29,861
What is it?
什么事？

210
00:14:30,048 --> 00:14:30,973
Nothing, come on.
没什么, 快点

211
00:14:42,835 --> 00:15:07,132
This is your Controller speaking.
There is no need for alarm.
这里是你们的管理员在讲话．没有必要惊慌

212
00:14:42,835 --> 00:14:48,132
You may all continue your work and play,
confident that the best is being done for you.
你们全都可以继续工作或者娱乐, 相信给你们准备的都是最好的

213
00:14:48,835 --> 00:14:56,132
But our unfortunate companion Medok
has been allowed to escape.
但我们不幸的同伴 Medok 被人放走了

214
00:14:57,235 --> 00:14:59,932
Emergency Patrols two and three are
now searching the Colony
紧急巡逻队二号三号正在搜索

215
00:15:00,035 --> 00:15:02,532
and he is sure to be caught before it is dark.
肯定可以在天黑前抓住他

216
00:15:02,835 --> 00:15:07,132
Now return to your work and play
with fresh heart and renewed energy!
现在回到你们工作和娱乐中去吧, fixme

217
00:15:08,292 --> 00:15:10,897
They got that bloke all over the place
like a blinking politician.
他们这里到处都有那个家伙, 像个闪耀的政客一样

218
00:15:11,224 --> 00:15:15,006
He is our controller. We are always pleased to see him.
He brings us encouragement.
他是我们的管理员．我们很乐意见到他．他给我们鼓励

219
00:15:15,213 --> 00:15:16,357
Oh, he's not a politician then!
噢, 那他不是一个政客

220
00:15:18,692 --> 00:15:23,892
Number nine shift to stand by.
Leader to report to Youth Centre.
第九班次请做好准备．队长到青年中心报到

221
00:15:24,362 --> 00:15:25,571
Work shift ready to leave.
工作班次准备离开

222
00:15:25,778 --> 00:15:26,865
"We're happy to work,
"我们乐于工作

223
00:15:27,165 --> 00:15:28,549
Happy to play,
乐于娱乐

224
00:15:28,788 --> 00:15:30,123
That's a nice wee tune Doctor.
这个小调挺不错, 博士

225
00:15:30,325 --> 00:15:31,553
Yeah, if you happen to like work.
是, 前提是你确实很喜欢工作

226
00:15:31,749 --> 00:15:33,802
It's a privilege to work for the Colony.
在殖民地工作是一项特权

227
00:15:34,080 --> 00:15:36,571
Shift leader reporting: Shift number nine,
all present and correct.
班次队长报告：第九班次, 全部到齐且正常

228
00:15:36,743 --> 00:15:38,739
Good. You're the first of the night shift.
很好．你是夜间班次的第一个

229
00:15:39,101 --> 00:15:42,544
Uh, what do ye do then? Farming or fishing?
哈, 你们做什么呢？农耕还是钓鱼？

230
00:15:43,513 --> 00:15:45,064
We work very hard here.
我们在这里很努力地工作

231
00:15:45,565 --> 00:15:47,726
Yes, but what do you do?
是, 但你们具体做什么？

232
00:15:48,809 --> 00:15:50,616
We tap and refine gas.
我们采集并提炼瓦斯

233
00:15:51,659 --> 00:15:52,710
For heating?
为了供热？

234
00:15:53,157 --> 00:15:55,935
No, we use it for many things.
The Colony depends on it.
不, 我们用在很多方面．殖民地依赖于它

235
00:15:56,157 --> 00:15:57,635
It's absolutely essen...
这东西绝对重要...

236
00:15:58,034 --> 00:16:01,231
Emergency! Quick, give me that! Come on!
紧急情况！快, 把那个给我！快点！

237
00:16:01,482 --> 00:16:03,926
Accident! Stand by, oxygen supply.
出事故了！准备氧气供应

238
00:16:04,482 --> 00:16:05,926
Take them away. Any other losses?
把他们带走, 还有其它损失吗？

239
00:16:06,233 --> 00:16:07,629
Two with gas sickness. Come on.
有两个被瓦斯喷晕了, 快点

240
00:16:07,935 --> 00:16:09,051
What happened?
发生了什么事？

241
00:16:09,274 --> 00:16:12,244
Their work. It can't be helped.
The work must be done.
他们的工作．fixme．工作必须完成

242
00:16:12,529 --> 00:16:15,070
Do you hear that, Doctor?
你听到了吗, 博士？

243
00:16:15,672 --> 00:16:17,001
Where's he gone?
他去哪儿了？

244
00:16:24,363 --> 00:16:26,359
Shh! I saw you.
嘘！我看见你了

245
00:16:26,595 --> 00:16:27,331
Get out!
出去！

246
00:16:27,567 --> 00:16:32,550
Oh, that's not very polite.
I was interested in what you were saying.
哦, 那可不太礼貌．我对你之前的话很感兴趣

247
00:16:32,849 --> 00:16:34,075
Who else knows I'm here?
还有谁知道我在这里？

248
00:16:34,354 --> 00:16:36,657
No one. Why should I tell them?
没谁．我为什么要告诉他们？

249
00:16:36,754 --> 00:16:43,657
Now these creatures - have you seen them clearly?
What do they look like?
现在说说那些怪物 - 你看清楚它们了吗？它们是什么样子的？

250
00:16:43,820 --> 00:16:44,974
What has it to do with you?
这跟你有什么关系？

251
00:16:45,183 --> 00:16:47,839
Well, I'm interested. What do they look like?
哦, 我感兴趣．它们是什么样子的？

252
00:16:48,193 --> 00:16:52,829
All right. If you really want to know.
好吧, 如果你非想知道．

253
00:16:53,193 --> 00:16:57,829
It's hard to say. They move at night, in the dark.
不太好说．它们在晚上移动, 在暗处

254
00:16:58,193 --> 00:17:02,829
And look horrible. Creatures... like giant insects.
而且看起来很吓人．那些怪物...就像巨型的虫子

255
00:17:03,467 --> 00:17:05,040
With big claws?
带有大螯？

256
00:17:05,369 --> 00:17:06,434
Yes, that's it.
是的, 就是它

257
00:17:07,456 --> 00:17:08,854
You've seen them in the Colony?
你在殖民地见过它们？

258
00:17:09,046 --> 00:17:09,800
Oh yes.
是的

259
00:17:10,406 --> 00:17:11,683
Has anyone else seen them?
还有其他人见到吗？

260
00:17:12,033 --> 00:17:16,130
A few, but they've lock them up in the correction hospital.
有几个, 但他们都被关起来了, 关在矫正医院

261
00:17:16,460 --> 00:17:17,807
Why do they do that?
他们为什么那么干？

262
00:17:18,065 --> 00:17:20,949
Control tells them to.
They'll put me back there when they catch me.
管理员让他们干的．等他们抓到我, 也会把我放到那里去的

263
00:17:22,917 --> 00:17:24,991
And they'll put you back there for helping me.
而且他们会把你放到那里去帮助我

264
00:17:25,331 --> 00:17:26,747
Doctor! Doctor!
博士！博士！

265
00:17:26,913 --> 00:17:28,464
Go on! Quickly! They're looking for you!
继续！快点！他们在看着你们呢！

266
00:17:28,689 --> 00:17:29,836
Doctor!
博士！

267
00:17:36,828 --> 00:17:39,283
But we searched there, I'm sure.
但我们搜过那里了, 我确定

268
00:17:39,597 --> 00:17:40,338
Aye.
是

269
00:17:44,941 --> 00:17:45,696
Were you looking for me?
你们是在找我吗？

270
00:17:45,929 --> 00:17:46,776
Where have you been?
你去哪里了？

271
00:17:47,043 --> 00:17:48,270
I'm just looking around, that's all.
我只是四周看看, 仅此而已

272
00:17:48,525 --> 00:17:50,626
It's dangerous to go off on your own after dark.
天黑之后一个人乱走是很危险的

273
00:17:50,881 --> 00:17:52,171
Oh, I'm used to the dark. I like it.
哦, 我已经习惯了黑夜了．我喜欢它

274
00:17:52,397 --> 00:17:56,005
We're confined to rest cubicles at night
by order of Control.
夜间我们得待在休息间里面, 这是管理员的命令

275
00:17:56,397 --> 00:18:00,005
Anyone who wanders around the Colony at night...
may be killed.
任何人如果在夜间在殖民地闲逛...可能会被杀

276
00:18:01,992 --> 00:18:07,906
Curfew time. All personnel not on duty
must retire to quarters.
宵禁时间到了．所有不在值班的人员必须返回住处

277
00:18:08,105 --> 00:18:09,164
Do you hear that?
你们听到了吗？

278
00:18:09,373 --> 00:18:12,916
Emergency patrols two and three to remain on duty.
紧急巡逻队二号和三号继续原任务

279
00:18:13,173 --> 00:18:16,916
Work shifts to remain at their posts until dawn.
工作班次人员继续在原岗位直到黎明

280
00:18:17,173 --> 00:18:21,916
Visitors to retire for the night to
the refreshing department.
访客们夜间退回到休息室

281
00:18:22,168 --> 00:18:24,579
That's you. You're confined here.
说你们呢．你们被限制待这里了

282
00:18:27,855 --> 00:18:29,059
Here we are, Doctor.
我们到了, 博士

283
00:18:29,317 --> 00:18:31,339
Your young friends are in their rooms over there.
你的年轻朋友们都在那边, 在他们自己的房间里了

284
00:18:31,580 --> 00:18:32,352
Thank you.
谢谢你

285
00:18:33,271 --> 00:18:35,219
I, er, I hope you sleep well.
我, 呃, 我期望你睡个好觉

286
00:18:35,406 --> 00:18:38,341
Oh, I'm sure I will. Thank you. Goodnight.
噢, 我肯定会的．谢谢你．晚安

287
00:18:38,619 --> 00:18:39,464
Goodnight, Doctor.
晚安, 博士

288
00:19:07,025 --> 00:19:14,381
It is now dark. No one will go outside into the Colony.
A dangerous man is in hiding.
现在天黑了．谁都不能出去在殖民地乱跑．有一个危险人物还躲藏着

289
00:19:14,525 --> 00:19:20,381
Our patrols have orders to shoot on sight.
Happy sleep time everybody.
我们的巡逻队收到了格杀勿论的命令．各位睡个好觉

290
00:19:21,124 --> 00:19:22,279
And the same to you!
对你也是一样！

291
00:20:54,585 --> 00:20:55,606
I'll have a look over there.
我要过去那边看一眼

292
00:20:56,663 --> 00:20:58,048
It's all right. It's me. Stay where you are.
没事的, 是我．待在原地别动

293
00:20:59,193 --> 00:20:59,862
Why are you back?
你回来做什么？

294
00:21:00,234 --> 00:21:00,875
Don't move.
别动

295
00:21:01,481 --> 00:21:03,464
Have a look in those new houses they're building.
看看他们正在建设的新房子

296
00:21:03,660 --> 00:21:04,927
He's coming! We'll have to get out!
他来了！我们必须出去！

297
00:21:05,152 --> 00:21:06,926
Wait! If he comes in this way, we'll go out the back.
等等！如果他从这边来, 我们就从外面回去

298
00:21:07,052 --> 00:21:08,826
If he comes in the back, we'll go out here.
如果他从后面过来, 我们就从这里出去

299
00:21:09,019 --> 00:21:12,518
He's coming... to the front of the house.
他来了...走房子的前面来的

300
00:21:13,601 --> 00:21:15,413
Over here. I heard something.
这里．我听到了什么

301
00:21:16,785 --> 00:21:17,940
All right. Go back.
好吧, 回去

302
00:21:18,140 --> 00:21:19,078
You can't stay here.
你们不能待在这里

303
00:21:19,263 --> 00:21:20,431
I'll try to create a diversion.
我去试试把他引开

304
00:21:20,586 --> 00:21:21,291
No, they'll kill you!
不, 他们会杀死你的！

305
00:21:21,490 --> 00:21:22,381
Do as I tell you.
按我告诉你的做

306
00:21:23,742 --> 00:21:24,865
Thanks.
谢谢

307
00:21:25,108 --> 00:21:27,001
Go on. Go on.
继续, 继续

308
00:21:33,578 --> 00:21:36,652
All right, we'll go through this opening
when I give the word.
好吧, 等我发话, 我们从这个门进去

309
00:21:39,706 --> 00:21:41,040
Right. Now!
好, 走！

310
00:21:41,738 --> 00:21:44,312
No, look. Out there.
不, 看, 那边

311
00:21:44,938 --> 00:21:45,775
I don't see anything.
我什么也没看见

312
00:21:45,982 --> 00:21:50,213
In that patch of moonlight. I told you I'd seen them!
在那边月光下．我说过我见过它们的！

